intent.user_query: Determine which product brand has the highest average price.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT Brand, AVG(Price) AS AveragePrice FROM fitness_db.Products GROUP BY Brand ORDER BY AveragePrice DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY AveragePrice DESC) <= 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT Brand, AVG(Price) AS AveragePrice FROM fitness_db.Products GROUP BY Brand ORDER BY AveragePrice DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY AveragePrice DESC) <= 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
